Gerard Horan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gerard_Horan 0 Gerard James Pertwee Horan (born 11 November 1962 in Stockport, Cheshire) is an English actor. He is known for playing Firefighter Leslie "Charisma" Appleby in London's Burning from 1986 to 1989 and again in 1994.
